        <!--Item 1: Exterior Window Cleaning-->
        <div>
            <h2>Exterior Window Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Restore the shine of your windows from the outside, removing dirt, dust, and grime for a spotless finish.</p>
            <img src="/Alex6.jpeg" alt="Exterior Cleaning image">
            <p>Our thorough exterior window cleaning service ensures your windows shine from the outside in. Using professional-grade tools and eco-friendly cleaning solutions, we remove dirt, dust, and debris that build up from weather exposure, leaving your windows streak-free and sparkling. This service not only improves the look of your home but also helps protect your windows from long-term damage.</p>
        </div>
                          

        <!--Item 2: Interior Window Cleaning--> 
        <div>
            <h2>Interior Window Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Let in more light with crystal-clear windows on the inside, free from smudges, fingerprints, and streaks.</p>
            <img src="image.jpg" alt="Interior Cleaning image">  
            <p>Enjoy spotless windows inside your home or office with our interior window cleaning. We use gentle, non-toxic products to eliminate smudges, fingerprints, and any buildup on the glass, giving your space a cleaner, brighter feel. Whether you're preparing for guests or want to improve your view, our team ensures every window is crystal clear.</p>
        </div>
            
        
        <!--Item 3: Track Cleaning-->
        <div>
            <h2>Window Track Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Ensure smooth operation of your windows by cleaning the tracks and preventing buildup.</p>
            <img src="window-track.jpg" alt="Window Track Cleaning image">
            <p>Over time, dirt, dust, and debris can collect in window tracks, making it harder to open or close the windows. Cleaning the tracks removes this buildup, helping the windows slide smoothly and function properly. Regular track cleaning not only prevents damage to the windows and frames but also ensures better airflow and overall efficiency in your home.</p>
        </div>
        

        <!--Item 4: Frame Cleaning-->
        <div>
            <h2>Window Frame Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Keep your window frames looking fresh and free of dirt and grime.</p>
            <img src="window-frame.jpg" alt="Window Frame Cleaning image">
            <p>Over time, dirt, dust, and other debris can accumulate on window frames, causing them to look dingy and unkempt. Our window frame cleaning service thoroughly removes buildup from all types of frames, ensuring they look as good as new. Clean frames not only improve the appearance of your windows but also prevent damage from the buildup of dirt and moisture, extending the lifespan of both your windows and their frames.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <!--Item 5: Screen Cleaning-->
        <div>
            <h2>Screen Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Keep your screens looking fresh and debris-free, allowing for clearer views and better airflow.</p>
            <img src="image.jpg" alt="Screen Cleaning image">
            <p>Dirty screens can block airflow and obscure your view. Cleaning the screens removes dust, dirt, and pollen, ensuring they look great and function properly. Clean screens improve air quality and allow more light to flow through, making your home or workspace feel fresher and more inviting.</p>
        </div>
           

        <!--Item 6: Solar panel cleaning-->
        <div>
            <h2>Solar Panel Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Ensure optimal performance of your solar panels by keeping them clean and free of debris.</p>
            <img src="solar-panel.jpg" alt="Solar Panel Cleaning image">
            <p>Dirty solar panels can reduce their efficiency by blocking sunlight and causing overheating. Our solar panel cleaning service removes dirt, dust, and other buildup, improving energy production and extending the lifespan of your panels. Clean panels can increase efficiency by up to 30%, allowing your home to save on electricity costs while contributing to a more sustainable environment.</p>
        </div>
        

        <!--Item 7: Hard Water Removal-->
        <div>
            <h2>Hard Water Removal</h2>
            <p>Keep your windows spotless by removing hard water stains and buildup.</p>
            <img src="hard-water.jpg" alt="Hard Water Removal image">
            <p>Our hard water removal service for windows eliminates stubborn mineral deposits, restoring clarity and shine to your glass. By removing these stains, we help maintain the longevity of your windows and prevent the buildup from damaging the surface, ensuring your home always has a crystal-clear view.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

